title: Dir En Grey - DUM SPIRO SPERO (2 CD Deluxe Edition)
description:
Dum Spiro Spero is the eighth studio album by the Japanese metal band Dir En Grey, released on August 3, 2011. 

Disc 1 is MP3 format, Disc 2 is FLAC (sorry, had to piece these together from various locations, if I can find a FLAC rip I'll pull this torrent and add an updated one.) The bitrates for the MP3s are variable, most at or above 260kbps.

I also plan to upload the 3rd disc of the deluxe edition if this torrent gets any attention, which is a DVD.

Please seed as long as you can! My upload speed is about 250Kbps so it'll take some time, but the other torrent of this album is apparently dead, and I'll be seeding this one vigilantly.
